类 MangoBaseListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • cn.ficos.Compiler.Syntax.MangoBaseListener
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    MangoListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    直接已知子类:
    ClassCollector, Field_FunctionCollector

    public class MangoBaseListener
extends java.lang.Object
implements MangoListener
    This class provides an empty implementation of MangoListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
